OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775412669
OL,3,CSeat cushion from the Titanic expected
OL,4,Cto fetch up to #180,000 at auction
OL,6,FThe cushion itself, made of canvas,
OL,7,Fwas taken from one of its 13 lifeboats
OL,8,Fthat brought survivors to the rescue
OL,9,Fship, SS Carpathia.
OL,11,FIt comes complete with four brass
OL,12,Feyelets in tact, and crucially it
OL,13,Fstill has its original lifeboat plaque
OL,14,Fand is being sold alongside an
OL,15,Foriginal length of rope from the ship
OL,16,Fand documents to verify its
OL,17,Fauthenticity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
