PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775412669
OL,3,CSeat cushion from the Titanic expected
OL,4,Cto fetch up to #180,000 at auction
OL,6,FAccording to the story told by
OL,7,Fauctioneers Henry Aldridge & Son, a
OL,8,Fcoffee and tea importer from London
OL,9,Fcalled Richard William Smith was
OL,10,Fsailing on the ill-fated liner to meet
OL,11,Fhis friend Mr TG Matthews, a fellow
OL,12,Ftea importer in Brooklyn, New York.
OL,14,FMr Smith was among the 1,500 who died
OL,15,Fin the disaster, although his body was
OL,16,Fnever identified.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
