OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775412669
OL,3,CSeat cushion from the Titanic expected
OL,4,Cto fetch up to #180,000 at auction
OL,6,F"The item can actually be identified
OL,7,Fon a period photograph of Titanic's
OL,8,FLifeboat 2.
OL,10,F"The item has been featured in one of
OL,11,Fthe most important books on Titanic
OL,12,Fmemorabilia written 'Fortune and Fate'
OL,13,Fand has a peer reviewed provenance
OL,14,Fpackage.
OL,16,F"It's truly a once-in-a-lifetime
OL,17,Fopportunity for a museum or collector."
OL,19,FThe seat cushion is going under the
OL,20,Fhammer at Henry Aldridge & Son of
OL,21,FDevizes, Wiltshire, on April 18.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOUyD@gO]
